{
  "texts": [
    "Results, ideally, should be organized in a tabulated format.",
    "Based on the preliminary suggestions from ChatGPT, users can eliminate superfluous or redundant lectures and recommend topics for inclusion.",
    "As a culmination of this phase, users can request ChatGPT to provide pedagogical strategies that resonate with the course's learning outcome and assessment methods and foster active student engagement during lectures.",
    "Should the user determine that the course's active learning strategies and assessment methods do not coherently align with the course schedule, they can submit a revised prompt for further refinement.",
    "This iterative process continues until the user deems the outputs from ChatGPT to be in congruence with all pivotal areas of the course."
  ]
}